      "title": "A1C limitation vs CGM",
      "claim_zh": "虽然HbA1c反映过去2-3个月的平均血糖，但它无法识别血糖波动以及日内和日间血糖变异的幅度和频率。",
      "claim_en": "While A1C reflects average glucose over the last 2-3 months, it fails to identify glycemic excursions and the magnitude and frequency of intra- and interday glucose variation.",
